data.description: Beautiful West Ridge 2 flat just steps to Devon and California! Both units feature 2 bedroom and 1 bathroom layouts. Huge living rooms, one with hardwood flooring and one carpeted, provide tons of natural light and include an attached dining area. The spacious kitchens with table space give access to the private decks overlooking a lovely yard and the parking pad with space for 5 cars. Bonus basement unit features a huge living room and kitchen with 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom. The common laundry area has 2 washers new in 2020, dryer and sink. Incredible location close to restaurants, shopping, and parks! Tenant occupied - 24 hour notice required.
